                      </a>
                      <a id="link-to-profile" class="stop-fetch" href="" class="stop-fetch" style="text-decoration: none; display: flex; flex-flow: column nowrap; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                           <svg <% /* eslint-disable-next-line css-propertyvalueexpected */ %> xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="fill: <%= user.userColor %>;transform: msFilter"><path d="M19 2H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v13a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4l3 3 3-3h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zm-7 3c1.727 0 3 1.272 3 3s-1.273 3-3 3c-1.726 0-3-1.272-3-3s1.274-3 3-3zM7.177 16c.558-1.723 2.496-3 4.823-3s4.266 1.277 4.823 3H7.177z"></path></svg>
                           <h3 <% /* eslint-disable-next-line css-propertyvalueexpected */ %> style="font-size: .9rem; color: <%= user.userColor %>;">Profile</h2>
